#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630002
#: 631c412663164bec8f46f624d3946586
msgid "Excluding Variables from Sampling with `MaskedPrior`"
msgstr "Excluyendo variables del muestreo con `MaskedPrior`"

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630004
#: c858eb7b3ef745c19f53e3d7870efa8d
msgid ""
"When models grow across many dimensions — countries, regions, product types,"
" and channels — not every combination is meaningful or even observed in the "
"data. For instance, some products may not be sold in certain countries, or "
"some channels may not operate in specific regions. In those cases, it’s "
"inefficient (and potentially misleading) to assign priors and sample "
"parameters for every combination. That’s where **`MaskedPrior`** comes in."
msgstr ""
"Cuando los modelos crecen en muchas dimensiones — países, regiones, tipos de"
" productos y canales — no todas las combinaciones son significativas o "
"incluso observadas en los datos. Por ejemplo, algunos productos pueden no "
"venderse en ciertos países, o algunos canales pueden no operar en regiones "
"específicas. En esos casos, es ineficiente (y potencialmente engañoso) "
"asignar priors y muestrear parámetros para cada combinación. Ahí es donde "
"entra **`MaskedPrior`**."

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630006
#: 7373e9dacadf45a9bc0a337bbee75cd2
msgid ""
"`MaskedPrior` allows you to define priors only over the *active* subset of "
"your parameter space.   You provide it with:"
msgstr ""
"`MaskedPrior` le permite definir priors solo sobre el subconjunto *activo* "
"de su espacio de parámetros. Usted le proporciona:"

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630008
#: 305f0c2432c94105a97401ca4ffb500b
msgid ""
"a **base prior** (e.g., `Prior(\"Normal\", mu=0, sigma=1, dims=(\"country\","
" \"channel\"))`), and"
msgstr ""
"una **base previa** (por ejemplo, `Prior(\"Normal\", mu=0, sigma=1, "
"dims=(\"country\", \"channel\"))`), y"

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630009
#: 5959b2828fbc475798dbf4812e803faf
msgid ""
"a **boolean mask** (`xarray.DataArray`) indicating which parameter entries "
"should be active (`True`) or excluded (`False`)."
msgstr ""
"una **máscara booleana** (`xarray.DataArray`) que indica qué entradas de "
"parámetro deben estar activas (`True`) o excluidas (`False`)."

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630011
#: f0001cbe9d58427aa1936cb0ecd63e52
msgid "Internally, `MaskedPrior` performs three main steps:"
msgstr "Internamente, `MaskedPrior` realiza tres pasos principales:"

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630012
#: 21a53f8047014fc1a306d19d158ac7c4
msgid ""
"**Subset creation:** It builds a reduced variable over only the active "
"entries (those marked `True` in the mask)."
msgstr ""
"**Creación de subconjuntos:** Se construye una variable reducida solo sobre "
"las entradas activas (aquellas marcadas como `True` en la máscara)."

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630013
#: 55fef3b5974e40fc97fc5408eae5b892
msgid ""
"**Sampling on active subset:** The sampler draws values only for this "
"smaller subset, ignoring inactive combinations completely."
msgstr ""
"**Muestreo en subconjunto activo:** El muestreador extrae valores solo para "
"este subconjunto más pequeño, ignorando completamente las combinaciones "
"inactivas."

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630014
#: 48f89d7f53f24c7a9a233c8f1e5c6f51
msgid ""
"**Expansion back to full shape:** The reduced variable is re-expanded to the"
" original dimensional shape, filling inactive positions with deterministic "
"zeros."
msgstr ""
"**Expansión de nuevo a la forma completa:** La variable reducida se "
"reexpande a la forma dimensional original, llenando las posiciones inactivas"
" con ceros deterministas."

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630016
#: 3bcf644e87f44fcda4ad8fd8edaa896e
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"See as the following, if you define a mask $M_{i,j} \\in \\{0,1\\}$ over a "
"parameter $\\theta_{i,j}$, the masked parameter becomes:"
msgstr ""
"Vea lo siguiente, si define una máscara $M_{i,j} \\in \\{0,1\\}$ sobre un "
"parámetro $\\theta_{i,j}$, el parámetro enmascarado se convierte en:"

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630018
#: 9a4a18a3068c4ffe8975bf91287ae39b
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\\tilde{\\theta}_{i,j} = \n"
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"\\theta_{i,j}, & \\text{if } M_{i,j} = 1, \\\\\\\\\n"
"0, & \\text{if } M_{i,j} = 0.\n"
"\\end{cases}\n"
msgstr ""
"\\tilde{\\theta}_{i,j} = \n"
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"\\theta_{i,j}, & \\text{if } M_{i,j} = 1, \\\\\\\\\n"
"0, & \\text{if } M_{i,j} = 0.\n"
"\\end{cases}"

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630026
#: 61cc959b795746b98623cb99504224c6
msgid "Sampling occurs only for the active subset:"
msgstr "La muestreo ocurre solo para el subconjunto activo:"

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630028
#: 34b6463562414d34abc9ccdc1bf87ee7
msgid ""
"\n"
"\\{\\theta_{i,j} : M_{i,j}=1\\},\n"
msgstr "\\{\\theta_{i,j} : M_{i,j}=1\\},"

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630032
#: 6c51e3b45dda40d492595a43287642c9
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"and the total number of random variables is reduced to $\\sum_{i,j} "
"M_{i,j}$."
msgstr ""
"y el número total de variables aleatorias se reduce a $\\sum_{i,j} M_{i,j}$."

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630034
#: 62f98e181ff44cf5b74886a6ff6993e8
msgid "The benefits are significant:"
msgstr "Los beneficios son significativos:"

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_gam_options.ipynb:630035
#: f0033981261b4ccbb1af0d55d4fcfe1a
msgid ""
"**Parameter reduction:** Only meaningful parameters are sampled, reducing "
"computational burden and improving sampling efficiency."
msgstr ""
"**Reducción de parámetros:** Solo se muestrean los parámetros "
"significativos, lo que reduce la carga computacional y mejora la eficiencia "
